item.title: new keyboard + update
item.author: Author
item.description: hey everybody! i’m back from the dead, once again. my last update was me complaining about myself being clumsy and pulling some liquids on my old keyboard, effectively killing it. i ended up digging my old keyboard research and settled on buying a HHKB professional classic in white from mechanicalkeyboards.com. let me tell you guys, this keyboard is a real joy to type on. it sounds really nice and satisfying to press all these buttons.
